OL,3,CPolice looking for killer after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death in Leicester
OL,6,FPolice in Leicester are appealing for
OL,7,Fwitnesses after a murder near the city
OL,8,Fcentre.
OL,10,FA man in his 20s was found with
OL,11,Fserious injuries to his stomach and
OL,12,Fchest at around 10.45 pm on Wednesday
OL,13,F23 July in London Road near Saxby
OL,14,FStreet.
OL,16,FLeicestershire Police say initial
OL,17,Fenquiries suggest the man was stabbed
OL,18,Fin De Montfort Place before he managed
OL,19,Fto flag down an officer who was
OL,20,Fdriving past.
