OL,3,CPolice looking for killer after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death in Leicester
OL,6,FHe was taken to hospital where he
OL,7,Flater died.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Lorna Granville
OL,10,Fsaid: "Our investigation is in the
OL,11,Fvery early stages, and we are
OL,12,Fcurrently working to establish the
OL,13,Ffull circumstances and identify those
OL,14,Fwho may have been involved.
OL,16,F"We believe the injured man may have
OL,17,Fbeen stabbed minutes before he was
OL,18,Fable to stop an officer who was
OL,19,Fdriving in the area.
